          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is this another conspiracy book?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>No. <em>The 2012 Blackfile™</em> is presented as a recovered intelligence-style document written in 2012, based on geopolitical modeling, early AI forecasting, and global risk assessments.<br/><br/>It’s not sensational or speculative, it’s analytical, structured, and eerily aligned with current world events.</p>",
            "page": ""
