          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How accurate are the predictions inside the book?",
            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p><br/>The Blackfile outlines trends that have since unfolded with alarming precision, pandemics, AI acceleration, global conflicts, misinformation waves, and migration patterns.<br/><br/>It does <strong>not</strong> claim supernatural foresight.<br/><br/>It is the result of early data modeling and pattern analysis.</p>",
