            "icon": "",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes.<br/><br/>The text is credited only to <em>“The Unknown Analyst, 2012.”</em><br/><br/>Their identity has never been confirmed, and surviving fragments of their digital footprint suggest they intentionally erased themselves after releasing the report.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
